\par
    -CompanyFax <String>\par
        Company Fax to use for the Cover Page   If the Cover Page has the Fax field.\par
\par
        The following Cover Pages have a Fax field:\par
                Contrast (Word 2010)\par
                Exposure (Word 2010)\par
\par
